ame such as “Swift Development Toolchain 2023-01-01 (a)”."}]},{"text":"Running tests","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Running-tests"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Navigate to the directory containing your package and run the following command:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["swift test"],"syntax":"sh"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift Package Manager will build and run a test target that uses the testing","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"library as well as a separate target that uses XCTest. To only run tests written","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"using the testing library, pass "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"--disable-xctest"},{"text":" as an additional argument to","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"swift test"},{"type":"text","text":" command."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If your package does not explicitly list the testing library as a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"dependency, pass "},{"code":"--enable-experimental-swift-testing","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"swift test"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"command to ensure your tests are run."}]}],"type":"aside","name":"Note"},{"level":4,"anchor":"Swift-510","text":"Swift 5.10","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"As of Swift 5.10, the testing library is not integrated into Swift Package","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Manager, but a temporary mechanism is provided for developers who want to start","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"using it with their Swift packages and the Swift 5.10 toolchain.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Warning","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This functionality is provided temporarily to 